item.title: CVE-2016-8951|2024-09-17T03:32:58.866Z -- ibm -- emptoris%20strategic%20supply%20management
item.description: IBM Emptoris Strategic Supply Management Platform 10.0.0.x through 10.1.1.x is vulnerable to a denial of service attack. An attacker can exploit a vulnerability in the authentication features that could log out users and flood user accounts with emails. IBM X-Force ID: 118838.
